  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Poseidra Abyss, the Atlantean Dragon Deity",
      "effect": "3 Level 7 monsters\nOnce per turn, you can also Xyz Summon \"Poseidra Abyss, the Atlantean Dragon Deity\" by using 1 \"Atlantean\" or \"Mermail\" Xyz Monster you control. (Transfer its materials to this card.) Once per turn: You can detach 2 materials from this card and send 1 WATER monster from your hand or Deck to the GY; return up to 3 cards your opponent controls to the hand. If this Xyz Summoned card is sent to the GY: You can discard 1 card to the GY; Special Summon 3 Level 3 or lower Fish, Sea Serpent, and/or Aqua monsters from your hand and/or GY.",
      "official": false
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u6d77\u7687\u9f8d\u795e \u30dd\u30bb\u30a4\u30c9\u30e9\u30fb\u30a2\u30d3\u30b9",
